Daimler - over half units meet capital return goal . German industrial conglomerate Daimler - Benz AG said on Thursday that more than half of its 23 businesses had already reached or improved on its target 12 percent return on capital employed . " More than half have now matched or exceeded the target , " chief executive Juergen Schrempp told the interim results conference held in London . Schrempp said earlier that the group as a whole was on course to meet the 12 percent target in two years . - - Tony Roddam , London Newsroom + 44 171 542 4017 
